        Give The Lessons Specific Purpose
      %p Giving the students a sense of purpose in creating their lessons can benefit their motivation.
      %p= link_to("Give The Lessons Specific Purpose >", "http://upsidedownacademy.org/lessons/27_upside-down-academy_strategies-for-using-this-site_give-the-lessons-specific-purpose")

  %li
