      .header
        Individuals vs. Groups Creating Lessons
      %p There are benefits to having students create lessons as a group or as individuals.
      %p= link_to("Individual vs. Group Lessons >", "http://upsidedownacademy.org/lessons/29_upside-down-academy_strategies-for-using-this-site_individual-group-lessons")

